ActFederal Courts Act
SubjectCommissioners for Administering Oaths ** Federal Court **
PrecisOrder directing that commissions do issue under the Great Seal of Canada EMPOWERING FIVE OFFICERS of the Courts Administration Service to ADMINISTER OATHS and to take and receive affidavits, declarations and solemn affirmations, within or outside Canada, in or concerning any proceeding had or to be had in the FEDERAL COURTS.
